snippet.textDisplay: Ye shirk he. Hum mola Ali se nahi mangte, Nabi pak s a w se bhi nahi mangte, taajdaare haram se nahi mangte, hum aap s a w par daruud bhejte hen. Hum sirf aor sirf Allah se mangte hen. Qabar walon se nahi mangte. Shirk sub se barha gunah. Ye dunia, hum sub, ye har cheez sirf Allah ne banaai he. Insaan kuch nahi bana sakta, bus Allah ki banai hui cheezon ko mila kar Allah ke diye hue dimaagh ki madad se use karta. Hum ek temporary time ke liye hen iss dunia me. Aor har nabi ne apne logon ko yehi bataya. Coke studio apne plate form ko ibadat bana sakta e aor daawat ka behtareen zareea. Agar shirkia poetry chorh de.
